<p>This <ref type="text" xml:id="r01" target="#q01">prose narrative (probably describing the battle of White Oak Swamp)</ref> is the basis for the poem "A March in the Ranks Hard-Prest, and the Road Unknown," which first appeared in <hi rend="italic">Drum-Taps</hi>(<date when="1865">1865</date>). <ref type="work" xml:id="r02" target="http://www.whitmanarchive.org/works/xxx.00188"/>
</p>
</work>
</relations>
